			</td>
			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There aren't any memory limitations if you're using custom hardware. It's easier to build a simple board with tons of ROM space than it is to build one with Everdrive-like features.<br /><br />UNROM can handle 4 MB. If NESmaker supports UNROM just make one of those. That's a ton of space.</div>

